### Frontend

#### [NEW] `frontend/src/pages/SearchPage.jsx`
- Full-page search experience:
  - Hero search bar with debounced input (300ms)
  - Left filter sidebar:
    - Level checkboxes (Beginner / Intermediate / Advanced)
    - Price range slider (`min_price` / `max_price`)
    - Language dropdown
    - Free-only toggle
    - Sort dropdown (Newest / Price ↑↓ / Rating)
  - Right results grid:
    - Course cards with thumbnail, title, mentor, avg rating stars, price, enrollment count
