## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```powershell
.venv\Scripts\python manage.py test courses.tests --verbosity=2
```
Tests will cover:
- Keyword search returns matching courses (title, description, mentor)
- Level filter returns only correct level
- Price range filter (min/max)
- `is_free` filter
- `avg_rating` annotation is computed correctly
- Unapproved/unpublished courses are excluded from search results
- Pagination works correctly
- Empty results return `[]` not 500

### Manual Verification
1. Open `/search` — confirm skeleton loaders then results appear
2. Type in the search bar — confirm debounced live results update
3. Apply Level = Beginner filter — confirm only beginner courses shown
4. Set max price to 0 — confirm only free courses shown
5. Change sort to "Highest Rated" — confirm ordering is correct
6. Share the URL — confirm reloading restores exact same filters
